Task Description

1. create a form with 2 fields
2. first input should be just text input 
3. The second input should be textarea with a minimum 5 rows of space
4. you should create reusable button CSS styles with modifiers 
4.1 you should have 3 variants of the button (primary-blue, secondary-red, ghost-no color, the background color will appear after hovering on the button's area (light gray))
4.2 button should have different sizes (small medium large)

5. add table with 4 columns 
6. add functionality to set todo row as done
7. add functionality to delete todo row